description._content: Catalog #: 09_01125 Title: Kathryn Fritz Special Collection Photo San Diego California Additional Information: Two unidentified men seated on rocks. Handwritten inscription ""To Peggy regards 'Bob'"", Kathryn Fritz was a young woman residing in San Diego during the 1920s. She was an aviation enthusiast and acquaintance of Charles Lindbergh.
